article.description: — Joey Reilly scored 21 points as Sacred Heart beat Wagner 66-61 on Sunday.
article.headline: Sacred Heart defeats Wagner 66-61
article.story: FAIRFIELD, Conn. -- — Joey Reilly scored 21 points as Sacred Heart beat Wagner 66-61 on Sunday. Reilly also had three steals for the Pioneers (10-10, 4-1 Northeast Conference). Alex Sobel scored 14 points while shooting 5 of 7 from the field and 4 for 6 from the line, and added five rebounds. Aidan Carpenter had 12 points and was 4 of 8 shooting (2 for 4 from 3-point range). The Seahawks (9-8, 3-2) were led by Melvin Council Jr., who recorded 14 points, six assists and two steals. Julian Brown added 13 points for Wagner. Tyje Kelton also had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
